main.name: Keeton Martin
main.description: I am a software engineer and I've put together this page to showcase my work. Welcome to my home base on the internet
main.bio: I graduate(d) from Haverford College with a B.S. in Computer Science in May 2022. I've accepted a job offer at Salesforce as an engineer, starting in August 2022. I like to build things in Python, Java, Java/Typescript, and in my free time I like to do play and think about basketball, keyboards, and enjoy the great outdoors.
main.contactmessage: Feel free to reach out to me using this form and I'll get back to you ASAP.
